      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried that. i tried to buy something else, some kind of plushie or whatever, but it just feels fake. it doesn't bring him back. everything just feels pointless now. like i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't even mean anything anymore. i don't see the point in waking up tomorrow just to feel this void again.",
