    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't want tiny moments. i just want it to stop. the constant heaviness in my chest, the way i can't even breathe right because the air feels so heavy... it's exhausting. i'm so tired of fighting to feel okay when there's nothing left to fight for. i just want to let go of the weight for good. it feels like the only way to actually find peace.",
